          "effect": "The spy thrashes around and emits a tinny scream followed by a steady ticking sound. At the beginning of what would have been its next turn, the clockwork spy explodes, dealing 1d10 piercing damage in a 5-foot emanation (DC 16 basic Reflex save). Its gemstone is destroyed, along with any information contained inside it.",
